Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:07.43,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)\fs10\pos(330,191)}你有新邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,综上所述  活版印刷和指南针…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及火药合称文艺复兴时期的三大发明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于这些发明对历史发展的影响有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢  打个比方说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如从21世纪中选出三大发明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(256,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经连接装置就必有一席之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  这是非常重要的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(208,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经连接装置为人类社会带来了信息革命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒面面包两个  奶油蜜瓜包一个  还有草莓酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在午休时给我带到屋顶上来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢迟到的话  就准备当沙包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别那么害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是公共摄像机的死角  你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算啥啊  怎么只有一个炒面面包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经卖光了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连帮我们当个跑腿的都做不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  胖猪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天奶油蜜瓜包两个和草莓酸奶五杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了  不然就真的把你当沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是最后的最终机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的最终机会…意思都重复了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能现在说说罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Direct  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接连接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪公主学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(340,328)}Avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以教我制作虚拟角色的窍门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材质感总是表现不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色的光影要怎样处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边  是黑雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兴奋个什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的大人物怎么可能会注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概就只有这个地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里的身手是多么灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我才不需要现实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在这个时代还有实体的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有虚拟世界不就足够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快  我要加速得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是虚拟世界  还是现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超越所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达到无人能及的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极速！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你躲到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春午休不见了踪影  害我找了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,152级！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得分263万！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊  赶紧给我退出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么是我的自由  你少管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  你对我来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(321,328)}Link  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出连线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(327,328)}Link  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘技  强制退出连线  服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这里可是男厕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你怎么知道我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了  刚刚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  不如把他们的邮件交给学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以让他们停学  但之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要和阿拓商量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别跟阿拓说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  我打算就这样过完学生时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  像我这种人你就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少让我为你做点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是马铃薯沙拉和火腿奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是阿春你喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知不道歉不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千百合哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Direct  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接连接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,166级？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我还有谁能打出这种得分？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明只剩这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs15}VR：Virtual Reality的简称，即虚拟实境。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是比VR游戏的技术…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为自己能够不输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你打出那离谱的分数的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想「加速」得更快吗  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天午休时  来交谊厅找我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小哥是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道这里是高年级生的专属地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找他有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  能让他过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个除了插到脖子上去还有别的用途吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:57.81,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&90&\fad(500,0)\fs19\pos(338,131)}文件下载 - 安全警告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:57.81,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&90&\fad(500,0)\fs19\pos(487,161)}是否运行程序BB2039？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:57.81,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&90&\fad(600,0)\fs19\pos(351,242)}确定                     取消
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是情侣之间才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳烦你走这一趟  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs17}思考发声：不动嘴唇，通过连线装置对话的技术。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会思考发声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会  请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是精心设计的恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上来说就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(394,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  我要向你的神经连接装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发送一个应用程序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.88,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\pos(385,166)}是否运行程序BB2039？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.88,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\pos(333,207)}确定                            取消
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦接收它  你的现实将完全毁坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再以一种超乎想像的方式重构
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即我的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.24,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)\fs19\frx20\fry-9\frz-16\pos(345,77)}文件下载 - 安全警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.24,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)\fs25\frx15\fry-6\frz-16\pos(501,168)}是否运行程序BB2039？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.24,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,400)\fs27\frx21\fry-8\frz-20\pos(282,231)}确定{\r}                          {\fad(1000,400)\fs23\frx-6\fry-10\frz-20\pos(282,231)}取消
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如现实真能就此毁坏  这正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫Brain  Burst的程序…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功安装之后  我再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说安装可能会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accelerated…加速世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然没猜错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日的我在接受时  也考虑了将近两分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为说服你而准备的台词…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都浪费掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  别给我装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油蜜瓜包和草莓酸奶  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫荒谷  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从有田那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是有些误会  才把你从动物园…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到这所中学来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你都说啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只胖猪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机已到  快喊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频连线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频连线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要看我的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来刚好被公共摄像机拍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正身处于Brain  Burst的程序功能下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「加速」状态之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(301,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们超频连线者居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(311,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频连线者？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下周围是静止的  但事实并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蓝色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由多台架设于交谊厅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共摄像机录得的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重构出的3D影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(351,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再借由神经连接装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让思考得以加速的大脑观看影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速思考？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速的比率是平常的一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  现实的1秒相当于这里的1000秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即我们能体会到16分40秒的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要运用这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是快要被打到的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在致命的瞬间加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能利用大量的时间把握现状考虑对策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是绝对躲不开的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  别躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时更应该被打飞才对  春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要  这很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名学生通过躲进公共摄像机的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直得不到应有的处分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有着众多公共摄像机的大庭广众之下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经中了我的挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是反击的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…如果使用Brain  Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能打得赢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能赢得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你已经得到超乎常人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(358,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为一名超频连线者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会乖乖地接他一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的选择很明智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  就要让效果最大化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速状态取消后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要主动地向后面跳开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是学姐不是在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过要让效果最大化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自有打算  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  好好干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频退出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,327)}Burst  Out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超频退出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  只是擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过要获取最大的效果了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样荒谷就不会再出现在你面前  永远不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受这一拳辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后请你多多指教  春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(450,328)}Neuro  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到明天上学为止  都不能卸下神经连接装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.49,副本AWTXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\fs18\pos(447,185)}断开与全球互联网的连接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可以连上全球网络  一秒都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说午休的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你被那家伙打到飞了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那时的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那时受的伤？没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微擦到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  还好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级的黑雪公主和你直连是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些  昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊  正要回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  我看了前些日子的剑道大赛的录像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒  才一年级就已经拿到冠军了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  运气好罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也多亏阿千带便当来为我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得那么起劲原来是有了便当的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过阿春昨天不也吃了阿千手制便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送便当是阿拓的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿拓又怎么会知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道把荒谷的事说了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会送我便当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  有个想看的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  下次见
